casebody.data:
STATE EX REL. WASHINGTON
v.
FIRST DIST. COURT OF APPEALS 2018-1713 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 13, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, Donnelly, and Stewart, JJ., concur. Fischer and DeWine, JJ., not participating.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On respondents' motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion for the Supreme Court to take judicial notice denied as moot.
